title: Bug 116564 - Hyperlink builder title changes with settings
description: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", but it is changing with the settings.
OB: When I click on "OK" and reopen the hyperlink builder, its title becomes "www.actuate.com".
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on "OK" in the hyperlink builder.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder.

Actual result: The title of the hyperlink builder becomes "www.actuate.com".

Expected result: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
